  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个患者从社区到住院的完整流程图，重点展示access block机制——就是那些导致病人滞留在急诊或住院部的系统性障碍。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，access block是核心。起点是Community节点吗？患者通常先经过GP还是直接去急诊？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP / primary care",
        "ED arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两条路径都要保留——大部分走GP转诊，但也有人直接去急诊。GP和Community都要连到ED_Arrival。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP / primary care",
        "ED arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Community和GP都指向ED_Arrival。接下来是急诊内部的评估治疗环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED assessment & treatment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ED_Treat是关键的state节点。然后到Admission决策点，决定收住院还是出院。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED assessment & treatment",
        "Decision to admit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接ED_Treat到Admission。Inpatient stay作为下一个state节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Decision to admit",
        "Inpatient stay"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，但真正的瓶颈在出院环节。病人临床ready了，却因为两个主要constraints出不去——aged care placement和NDIS supports。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready for discharge",
        "Aged care placement",
        "NDIS supports / accommodation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个blockages都是capacity constraint类型？用risk样式区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aged care placement",
        "NDIS supports / accommodation",
        "constraints"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Block_Aged和Block_NDIS都是risk类，用虚线边框。它们从Ready节点分出来，表示出院受阻的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready for discharge",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "两个blockages已添加。现在画feedback loop——occupancy feedback loop从Block_Aged回到Inpatient？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "occupancy feedback loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这是核心机制：aged care堵了→病人滞留在住院部→床位占满→整个系统back pressure。用虚线表示这是间接反馈，不是流程前进。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "occupancy feedback loop",
        "feedback"
